Unit testing:
Unit testing means, test our own code like gave the token and waiting for the response whether we get
or not.

integration testing:
If i do more than one test cases together called integration testing.

System tester:
Done by tester(not developer), because they are testing throughout the system.

User Acceptance testing:
done by end user or end customer.

Eg: if im the user and im using amazon, if im trying to do something amazon and not able to do that, then
i report that amazon using call.


Mocha is a library that is used to run the test cases.
